        "faq_item_mXLRer": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is manufactured stone hard to maintain?",
            "answer": "<p>One of the benefits of Creative Mines stone and brick veneer is that it requires very little maintenance. If cleaning is needed, simply follow Creative Mines <a href=\"https://d2ho1mx8zrpzgz.cloudfront.net/pdfs/care-and-maintenance.pdf\">Care & Maintenance</a> guide.</p>",
