        },
        "faq_item_8iJQdT": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I clean manufactured stone or brick veneer?",
            "answer": "<p>Occasional cleaning with mild soap and water to remove surface dust and dirt is typically all that's required to keep the stone veneer looking its best. Download Creative Mines <a href=\"https://d2ho1mx8zrpzgz.cloudfront.net/pdfs/care-and-maintenance.pdf\">Care & Maintenance PDF</a>.</p>",
