        "faq_item_NFYPBA": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you provide digital tools or resources for design planning?",
            "answer": "<p>Creative Mines provides hatch patterns, seamless textures for CAD drawings which can be downloaded directly from our website or from <a href=\"https://architextures.org/textures\">https://architextures.org/</a> . If using architextures.org, please type in Creative Mines to find a full library of our seamless textures.</p>",
