          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer design consultations or samples for architects and designers?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, Creative Mines provides a variety or resources for the A&D community, including technical support, samples, project mock ups and design consultations.</p>",
