        "faq_item_gar7mz": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I request custom textures, colors, or profiles for a specific project?",
            "answer": "<p>Custom textures, colors, and profiles may be available depending on the project type, timeline, and scale. To explore custom options, consult your local Creative Mines Sales Representative for details and feasibility. Please fill out our <a href=\"/pages/start-project\">Start A Project</a> form to get started.</p>",
