          }
        },
        "faq_item_fbc8QY": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How does Pozzolan technology improve long-term durability and performance?",
            "answer": "<p>Pozzolan along with proprietary raw materials and processes, create a gladiator strong mix design that provides a high compressive strength and unmatched freeze-thaw durability in our products. As a result, Creative Mines products will outperform all other stone veneer products in the marketplace. See the test results <a href=\"/pages/resources/#technical\" title=\"/pages/resources/#technical\">here</a>.</p>",
            "faqvideo": "",
            "cat_option1": false,
            "cat_option2": false,
            "cat_option3": true,
            "cat_option4": false,
            "cat_option5": true,
            "cat_option6": false,
            "cat_option7": false,
            "cat_option8": false,
            "cat_option9": false,
            "cat_option10": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QGzmtd": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is the compressive strength or water absorption rate of your stone?",
            "answer": "<p>The compressive strength of Creative Mines stone veneer will average 3800 psi. The water absorption rate will average 17%. For a complete view of Creative Mines test results, click <a href=\"https://d2ho1mx8zrpzgz.cloudfront.net/pdfs/test-results-overview.pdf\">here</a>.</p>",
            "faqvideo": "",
            "cat_option1": false,
            "cat_option2": false,
            "cat_option3": true,
            "cat_option4": false,
