        "faq_item_nbLJ3T": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How are the masonry veneers adhered to wall surfaces?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Grouted Installations:</strong> Creative Mines recommends a Type N or S bonding mortar.</p><p><strong>Dry-stacked (Tight-fit) Installations:</strong> Creative Mines recommends a polymer modified mortar meeting ANSI A118.4 or A118.15.</p><p>It's important to follow the <a href=\"https://d2ho1mx8zrpzgz.cloudfront.net/pdfs/CMHA-MANUFACTURED-STONE-INSTALL-GUIDELINES-ENGLISH.pdf\">CMHA Installation Guidelines</a>.</p>",
