        "faq_item_EHFNQQ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are Creative Mines' masonry veneers suitable for both interior and exterior applications?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, our stone veneers are versatile and can be applied to both interior and exterior surfaces, allowing for cohesive design elements throughout your space. Since the wall preparation may differ, refer to the CMHA Installation Guidelines to ensure the wall is prepared in compliance with the installation guidelines.</p>",
