          "settings": {
            "question": "Are there specific considerations for installations over 30 feet in height?",
            "answer": "<p>For installations up to 30 feet in height over wood-frame construction, standard installation procedures are sufficient. For heights exceeding 30 feet or for installations over non-wood-framed sheathing, it's advisable to consult with a building code official or structural engineer to ensure compliance and safety.</p>",
