          "settings": {
            "question": "What maintenance is required after installation?",
            "answer": "<p>Manufactured stone is virtually maintenance-free. Occasional cleaning with mild soap and water to remove surface dust and dirt is typically all that's required to keep the stone looking its best. Visit our Creative Mines website for information on care & maintenance of our products.</p>",
