          "settings": {
            "question": "Do I need a professional mason to install your products?",
            "answer": "<p>A professional mason is always recommended, however is not required to install our products. If the installer has some general masonry skills and is an experienced DIY, a successful masonry installation can be achieved. Please follow the CMHA installation guidelines for proper install techniques, substrates, mortars and grout. You can download a copy <a href=\"https://d2ho1mx8zrpzgz.cloudfront.net/pdfs/CMHA-MANUFACTURED-STONE-INSTALL-GUIDELINES-ENGLISH.pdf\">here</a>.</p>",
