            "cat_option7_7": false,
            "cat_option8_7": false,
            "cat_option9_7": false,
            "cat_option10_7": false,
            "question_8": "Do you offer touch-up kits for chips or repairs?",
            "answer_8": "<p>Yes, Creative Mines can provide a repair or color touch-up kits should the product get accidentally damaged. Contact our customer service department at <a href=\"mailto:create@creativemines.us\">create@creativemines.us</a> to make a request. Please have the color and profile details to ensure you request the correct materials.</p>",
            "faqvideo_8": "",
